# Pixel Art: Cyberpunk Cityscape

**What:** A 64x64 pixel art depiction of a futuristic cyberpunk city at night, featuring neon-lit skyscrapers, holographic billboards, and rain-slicked streets reflecting vibrant colors.

**Why:** I chose this theme because cyberpunk aesthetics naturally lend themselves to striking pixel art—the high contrast between dark shadows and bright neon creates visual depth even at low resolution. The rain and reflections add atmosphere and demonstrate how limited pixels can evoke emotion and storytelling.

**File:** `cyberpunk_cityscape.png` (64x64 pixels, PNG format)